Package GUI

Class Summary
CancelButton This class creates a JButton with the text "Cancel", used to go back to "default-mode".
DeleteUserButton This class creates a JButton with the text "Delete", used to delete a user from the system.
EditUserButton This class creates a JButton with the text "Edit user", used to edit users.
LoadMoreResultsButton This class creates a new JButton with the text "Load more results", used to load more results in "search-mode".
Main This is the Main class, it launches the entire BicycleGarageManager system.
NewUserButton This class creates a JButton with the text "Create user", used to change to "create-mode".
OpenMenu This class creates a JMenuItem with the text "Open", used to open other storage files.
OperatorGUI This class creates the main Operator Interface.
PrintBarcodeButton This class creates a JButton with the text "Print barcode", used to print barcodes.
SaveAsMenu This class creates a JMenuItem with the text "Save as ...", used to save the storage file to a new location and/or with a new name.
SaveButton This class creates a new JButton with the text "Save", used to add users to the system.
SaveMenu This class creates a JMenuItem with the text "Save", used to save the storage file to its default location with its default name.
SearchButton This class creates a new JButton with the text "Search", used to query the system for information.
ViewUserButton This class creates a new JButton with the text "View", used to view a selected user's information.
